WEBVTT

00:02.330 --> 00:03.695
PREVIOUSLY ON "SALEM"...

00:03.730 --> 00:06.130
Isaac: SAW A DUSTY FELLA
WALKING INTO TOWN TODAY.

00:06.170 --> 00:07.899
I COULDN'T BELIEVE MY EYES.

00:07.940 --> 00:10.238
IT WAS JOHN ALDEN.

00:10.270 --> 00:12.135
Mary:
YOU TOLD ME HE WAS DEAD!

00:12.180 --> 00:13.807
John:
THIS IS MY VOW.

00:13.840 --> 00:15.376
I WILL COME BACK FOR YOU.

00:15.410 --> 00:16.900
Tituba:
WHAT'S JOHN ALDEN

00:16.950 --> 00:18.577
COMPARED TO ALL
THAT LIES BEFORE YOU?

00:18.610 --> 00:20.419
Mary:
[ SCREAMS, GASPS ]

00:20.450 --> 00:22.384
Giles:
YOU COME BACK FOR ONE THING
AND ONE THING ONLY.

00:22.420 --> 00:24.513
SHE'S MARY SIBLEY NOW.

00:24.550 --> 00:26.586
AND SHE'S THE RICHEST WOMAN
IN SALEM.

00:26.620 --> 00:29.054
Mary:
TIME FOR YOUR FEEDING.

00:29.090 --> 00:30.580
-George: [ GRUNTS ]
-Mary: [ GRUNTING ]

00:30.630 --> 00:31.881
[ STOMACH GURGLING ]

00:31.930 --> 00:33.852
George: [ GROANS ]

00:33.900 --> 00:38.792
Giles: PRECIOUS SALEM CAUGHT UP
IN A STINKING WITCH PANIC.

00:39.940 --> 00:42.602
Cotton: THE DEVIL
WAS NEVER GOING TO LET

00:42.640 --> 00:45.768
A PROMISED LAND BE BUILT HERE
WITHOUT A FIGHT!

00:45.810 --> 00:47.107
Man: [ SCREAMS ]

00:47.140 --> 00:48.277
Anne:
I'M NOT AFRAID OF THE DEAD,

00:48.310 --> 00:49.447
NOR THE LIVING FOR THAT MA'I'I'ER.

00:49.480 --> 00:50.742
Woman: [ SCREAMS ]

00:50.780 --> 00:52.338
John: WHAT IS IT
THAT TH ESE WITCHES WANT?

00:52.380 --> 00:54.268
Cotton:
A COUNTRY OF THEIR OWN.

00:54.320 --> 00:56.948
Mary: I WAITED FOR YOU.
YEARS AND YEARS.

00:58.220 --> 01:00.381
Giles: I WAS THERE
THE NIGHT YOU DID IT.

01:01.560 --> 01:03.357
Mary: IT'S ALL THAT I HAVE LEFI'
OF HIM.

01:03.390 --> 01:04.618
[ SCREAMS ]

01:04.660 --> 01:07.720
Giles:
THAT WAS JOHN ALDEN'S BABY.

01:07.760 --> 01:10.092
ARE YOU GONNA TELL HIM,
OR AM I?

01:11.900 --> 01:13.629
Cotton:
SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH.

01:13.670 --> 01:14.932
Mercy: [ SCREAMS ]

01:15.500 --> 01:17.309
Mary: WHO SAW US?

01:17.340 --> 01:19.808
Mr. Hale:
AND I WILL TELL YOU AGAIN.

01:19.840 --> 01:21.535
I DO NOT KNOW.

01:21.580 --> 01:23.207
Mary:
THE WITCH HUNT HAS BEGUN,

01:23.250 --> 01:25.104
AND WE WILL BE RUNNING
THE TRIALS.

01:25.150 --> 01:26.947
Cotton:
ARE YOU GUILTY...

01:26.980 --> 01:28.208
OR NOT?

01:28.250 --> 01:30.013
Giles: [ GROANS ]

01:34.190 --> 01:38.581
Cotton: MOST OF THOSE WHO HAVE
EVER LIVED ARE NOW DEAD.

01:38.630 --> 01:42.327
ALL BUT VERY FEW
MUST SURELY BURN IN HELL.

01:42.370 --> 01:47.137
WE MAY SOMEDAY OVER-PEOPLE
THIS VAST, EMPTY NEW LAND,

01:47.170 --> 01:50.560
BUT I FEAR THAT WE HAVE ALREADY
OVER-PEOPLED HELL.

01:50.610 --> 01:55.070
SO THAT,
AS IT IS WRITI'EN IN ISAIAH,

01:55.110 --> 01:57.442
"HELL HATH ENLARGED HERSELF."

01:57.480 --> 02:00.847
AND IS NOW CALLED...

02:00.880 --> 02:02.609
AM ERICA.

02:02.650 --> 02:05.483
I HAVE BEEN IN SALEM
A FORTNIGHT,

02:05.520 --> 02:08.455
AND I HAVE ALREADY
HUNG THREE WITCHES.

02:08.490 --> 02:12.028
IS THIS THE PRICE
OF BUILDING HEAVEN ON EARTH?

02:14.160 --> 02:17.425
I HAVE LAID MY HANDS UPON
HIS MOST DEADLY SERVANTS --

02:17.470 --> 02:19.961
THE WITCHES.

02:20.000 --> 02:22.662
OR HAVE I?

02:22.710 --> 02:25.463
I OBEYED
EVERY ONE OF YOUR INSTRUCTIONS.

02:25.510 --> 02:30.447
I EVEN PRESSED A POSSIBLY
INNOCENT MAN TO DEATH.

02:30.480 --> 02:34.109
I STILL TASTE HIS SPATI'ERED
BLOOD ON MY LIPS.

02:34.150 --> 02:37.119
PLEASE, LORD, I BEG THEE.

02:37.150 --> 02:39.710
GIVE ME A SIGN.

02:39.760 --> 02:41.648
[ SQUAWKS ]

02:45.430 --> 02:47.057
[ "CUPID CARRIES A GUN" PLAYS ]

02:53.070 --> 02:55.789
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

02:55.840 --> 02:57.398
* WITCH DRUMS

02:57.440 --> 03:00.034
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:01.280 --> 03:03.874
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:03.910 --> 03:05.309
* THE WITCH DRUMS

03:05.350 --> 03:07.875
* BETTER PRAY FOR HELL

03:07.920 --> 03:13.210
* NOT HALLELUJAH

03:43.390 --> 03:46.382
[ FLIES BUZZING ]

03:51.230 --> 03:53.892
[ WOOD CREAKS ]

04:02.810 --> 04:05.165
Isaac: [ GRUNTS ]

04:14.120 --> 04:16.418
FORGIVE ME.

04:16.450 --> 04:18.680
[ BUZZING CONTINUES ]

04:20.190 --> 04:22.181
[ BIRDS SQUAWK ]

04:32.540 --> 04:35.930
Gloriana: HAVE YOU
LOST YOUR LUST FOR LIFE?

04:35.970 --> 04:39.235
DON'T TELL ME
THAT YOU ARE FULL UP.

04:39.270 --> 04:42.842
Cotton: PERHAPS
SOME HOLES CANNOT BE FILLED.

04:42.880 --> 04:44.802
Gloriana: REALLY, MY LORD?

04:44.850 --> 04:47.341
WHICH HOLES ARE THOSE?

04:47.380 --> 04:49.985
Cotton:
THE ONES WE DIG FOR OURSELVES.

04:51.720 --> 04:54.109
Gloriana: WHAT WEIGHS SO HEAW
ON YOU, LOVE?

04:54.160 --> 04:57.027
Cotton: BY THE TASTE OF IT,
MY FATHER'S BOOT.

04:57.060 --> 04:58.823
Gloriana: [ LAUGHS ]

04:58.860 --> 05:01.124
YOU'RE A BIG BOY NOW.

05:01.160 --> 05:04.493
GROWN MEN
DON'T FEAR THEIR FATHERS.

05:04.530 --> 05:06.839
Cotton:
YOU DON'T KNOW MY FATHER.

05:06.870 --> 05:09.168
Gloriana:
EVERYONE KNOWS YOUR FATHER.

05:09.200 --> 05:11.168
Cotton: PRECISELY.

05:11.210 --> 05:12.529
Woman:
NO, YOU CAN'T GO IN THERE!

05:12.580 --> 05:14.309
Cotton: CAPTAIN ALDEN!

05:14.340 --> 05:16.274
NO! NO! NO!

05:16.310 --> 05:18.369
Gloriana: LEAVE HIM ALONE!

05:18.410 --> 05:21.573
John: GET OUT.

05:23.050 --> 05:26.213
THIS IS HOW YOU WIPE THE
INNOCENT BLOOD OFF YOUR HANDS?

05:26.250 --> 05:29.788
-ON THE ASS OF A WHORE?
-Cotton: GILES COREY NEVER PLED!

05:29.830 --> 05:33.618
ERGO, WE DON'T KNOW
HE WAS INNOCENT!

05:33.660 --> 05:35.059
[ SCREAMS ]

05:35.100 --> 05:37.728
John:
GIVE ME ONE GOOD REASON

05:37.770 --> 05:41.228
WHY I DON'T
PUT YOU IN THE GROUND.

05:43.770 --> 05:47.399
Cotton: SIR, I CANNOT.

05:47.440 --> 05:51.149
I'VE BEEN EXPECTING THE ANGEL
OF DEATH SINCE I WAS 10.

05:51.180 --> 05:53.978
I DIDN'T SEE HIM MYSELF,
BUT I KNEW FROM THE LOOK

05:54.020 --> 05:57.080
IN GRANDFATHER'S EYES
JUST BEFORE HE WENT,

05:57.120 --> 06:00.556
THE ANGEL
BORE A MOST TERRIBLE FACE.

06:02.630 --> 06:05.929
QUITE LIKE YOURS, I EXPECT.

06:05.960 --> 06:10.761
SO COME, ANGEL.

06:10.800 --> 06:12.392
YOU FIND ME FULLY PREPARED

06:12.440 --> 06:14.761
TO BURN LIKE A HUMAN CANDLE
FOR ETERNITY

06:14.800 --> 06:17.735
IN A PIT OF BURNING BLACK TAR
WITH ALL THE OTHER DAMNED.

06:19.810 --> 06:22.540
John: BURNING BLACK TAR?

06:22.580 --> 06:24.844
I THOUGHT HELL WAS FIRE.

06:24.880 --> 06:26.677
Cotton: A COMMON MISCONCEPTION.

06:26.720 --> 06:28.676
HELLFIRE BURNS LIKE FIRE

06:28.720 --> 06:31.644
BUT IS THE CONSISTENCY
OF THICK BLACK PITCH.

06:37.260 --> 06:38.784
WHAT?

06:38.830 --> 06:41.048
WHAT HAVE YOU SEEN?

06:43.600 --> 06:46.694
John: NOT SURE.

06:46.740 --> 06:50.961
HELL ON EARTH, MAYBE.

06:51.010 --> 06:54.400
GET DRESSED.

06:54.440 --> 06:56.442
I'VE GOT SOMETHING TO SHOW YOU.

06:56.480 --> 06:58.948
[ HORSE NEIGHS ]

07:01.150 --> 07:02.879
Cotton: WHERE ARE WE GOING?

07:02.920 --> 07:04.046
John: THE WOODS.

07:04.090 --> 07:05.489
Cotton: TO WHAT END?

07:05.520 --> 07:07.215
John: YOU HAVE
THE MORAL COMPASS OF A MEAT ANT,

07:07.260 --> 07:09.728
BUT YOU DO
KNOW SOMETHING ABOUT WITCHES.

07:09.760 --> 07:11.819
I SAW THEM.

07:11.860 --> 07:14.454
JUST LIKE MERCY LEWIS
DESCRIBED THEM.

07:14.500 --> 07:17.298
ANIMAL HEADS AND ALL.

07:17.330 --> 07:19.161
Mr. Hale: CAPTAIN ALDEN.

07:19.200 --> 07:23.068
AS MAGISTRATE OF SALEM,
I HEREBY PLACE YOU UNDER ARREST

07:23.110 --> 07:25.670
FOR VIOLENT REMONSTRATIONS
IN THE COMMON LAST NIGHT.

07:25.710 --> 07:30.170
YOU SHALL FACE CHARGES
OF DISORDERLY, RIOTOUS MISCHIEF

07:30.210 --> 07:32.770
AND INCITEMENT TO MAYHEM.

07:32.820 --> 07:35.971
John: TALK TO ISAAC.
HE'LL SHOW YOU THE WAY.

07:36.020 --> 07:38.818
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO, HALE?

07:38.850 --> 07:41.614
PRESS ME TO DEATH JUST LIKE
YOU DID TO GILES COREY?

07:41.660 --> 07:43.252
Mr. Hale: I SUGGEST YOU TAKE
THAT UP WITH YOUR NEW FRIEND,

07:43.290 --> 07:46.054
THE REVEREND,
AS IT WAS HIS DOING, NOT MINE.

07:48.200 --> 07:50.361
AWAY WITH HIM.

07:52.300 --> 07:53.961
[ GRUNTING ]

08:15.190 --> 08:17.351
Mary:
YOU'VE HAD A BUSY NIGHT.

08:18.930 --> 08:22.127
WHEN WERE YOU PLANNING TO TELL
ME YOU'D ARRESTED JOHN ALDEN?

08:22.160 --> 08:25.368
BEFORE OR AFTER YOU HANG HIM?

08:25.400 --> 08:27.868
Mr. Hale:
THE MAN IS A LOOSE CANNON.

08:27.900 --> 08:30.562
HE THREATENED THE SELECTMEN
IN FRONT OF HALF THE TOWN.

08:30.610 --> 08:34.376
Mary: IF HE'S A PROBLEM,
HE'S MY PROBLEM.

08:34.410 --> 08:36.298
Mr. Hale: WITH ALL DUE RESPECT,

08:36.340 --> 08:39.070
HE COULD BECOME A PROBLEM
FOR US ALL.

08:39.110 --> 08:44.184
Mary: MY HUSBAND CONTROLS SALEM,
AND I CONTROL HIM.

08:44.220 --> 08:47.553
YOU DO NOTHING WITHOUT MY SAY.

08:48.890 --> 08:51.324
WITH ALL DUE RESPECT.

08:51.360 --> 08:53.897
Mr. Hale: YES, MA'AM.

08:55.600 --> 08:58.728
Mary: CONCERN YOURSELF
WITH ONE THING, MR. HALE --

08:58.770 --> 09:01.591
FIND OUT WHO BROKE OUR CIRCLE.

09:01.640 --> 09:03.767
HEAD BACK TO THE WOODS.

09:03.810 --> 09:05.937
FIND THE SEER.

09:05.970 --> 09:08.575
HIS EYES WERE THERE.

09:24.090 --> 09:27.196
Isaac: IT WAS RIGHT HERE
WE SAW THE WITCHES.

09:27.230 --> 09:28.857
Cotton: CAPTAIN ALDEN
SAW ALL THIS, TOO?

09:28.900 --> 09:31.027
Isaac: YEAH.

09:31.070 --> 09:32.799
AND SOMETHING ELSE --

09:32.840 --> 09:35.138
SOMETHING I AIN'T SEEN BEFORE.

09:35.170 --> 09:37.934
THEY STABBED A BIRD --

09:37.970 --> 09:39.403
A WHITE DOVE.

09:44.280 --> 09:46.373
I KILLED
MORE THAN A FEW PIGEONS MYSELF,

09:46.410 --> 09:48.776
AND A DOVE AIN'T NOTHING
BUT A PRE'I'I'IER PIGEON,

09:48.820 --> 09:50.617
BUT THIS FELT DIFFERENT.

09:50.650 --> 09:53.380
I CAN'T SAY WHY --

09:53.420 --> 09:57.424
LIKE IT WAS THE SADDEST THING
IN THE WORLD...

09:57.460 --> 10:00.588
TO BLEED A DOVE TO DEATH.

10:00.630 --> 10:03.098
JUST THE ONE DOVE.

10:21.520 --> 10:25.616
Cotton: OF COURSE.
LIKE A WITCH'S CAULDRON.

10:30.290 --> 10:34.021
Isaac:
A TREE? LIKE A CAULDRON?

10:34.060 --> 10:36.893
AND FOLKS SAY ISAAC'S TOUCHED.

10:42.400 --> 10:45.062
Cotton: GOT YOU.

10:59.690 --> 11:01.783
[ GASPING ]

11:01.820 --> 11:03.253
[ PANTING ]

11:05.330 --> 11:07.150
Militia Man: MRS. SIBLEY.

11:07.200 --> 11:08.758
-Mary: OPEN IT.
-Militia Man: YES, MA'AM.

11:14.040 --> 11:16.190
Mary: NOW LEAVE.

11:22.010 --> 11:24.706
SALEM STILL HANGS MEN
FOR WHAT YOU DID --

11:24.750 --> 11:26.809
THREATENING THE SELECTMEN.

11:26.850 --> 11:28.909
John:
NOTHING STOPPING THEM.

11:28.950 --> 11:30.838
Mary:
I'D NEVER LET THAT HAPPEN.

11:30.890 --> 11:32.482
John:
AND WHERE WAS THAT COMPASSION

11:32.520 --> 11:34.715
WHEN GILES COREY
WAS BEING CRUSHED TO DEATH?

11:37.230 --> 11:39.482
Mary: YOU'RE FREE TO GO.

11:39.530 --> 11:43.261
BUT THE SELECTMEN URGE YOU TO
LEAVE SALEM AND NEVER COME BACK.

11:43.300 --> 11:44.562
John: THE SELECTMEN...

11:48.240 --> 11:50.606
...OR MARY SIBLEY?

11:50.640 --> 11:53.279
Mary:
I AM TRYING TO SAVE YOU.

11:53.310 --> 11:55.335
YOU DON'T BELONG HERE.

11:55.380 --> 11:57.405
John: AND NEITHER DO YOU.

11:57.450 --> 12:00.442
Mary:
I TOLD YOU -- I CAN'T LEAVE.

12:02.650 --> 12:04.379
John:
WELL, LAST TIME I CHECKED,

12:04.420 --> 12:07.389
YOUR HUSBAND WAS IN NO SHAPE
TO STOP YOU.

12:09.590 --> 12:11.126
Mary: [ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

12:11.160 --> 12:14.049
YOUR CONFIDENCE ASTOUNDS ME,
CAPTAIN.

12:14.100 --> 12:16.227
BUT DID YOU IMAGINE
THAT I WOULD WELCOME YOU BACK

12:16.260 --> 12:18.364
WITH TEARS OF JOY?

12:18.400 --> 12:21.130
HOW INCREDIBLY NAIVE YOU ARE.

12:21.170 --> 12:22.728
YOU'RE TOO LATE.

12:22.770 --> 12:24.601
IT'S OVER.

12:24.640 --> 12:27.177
I DON'T WANT YOU HERE.

12:29.340 --> 12:31.479
John: I ALMOST BELIEVE YOU.

12:33.180 --> 12:36.240
Mary: GET OUT OF SALEM --
NOW --

12:36.280 --> 12:38.510
OR YOU WILL HANG.

12:54.370 --> 12:55.997
Beggar Girl: SIR.

13:01.780 --> 13:03.270
[ GASPS ]

13:05.150 --> 13:07.471
[ GIRLS MURMURING ]

13:13.290 --> 13:15.713
Hannah: [ GROANING ]

13:18.660 --> 13:22.027
[ SCREAMING ]

13:22.060 --> 13:23.925
Bridget:
ALL RIGHT, YOU CAN DO THIS.

13:23.970 --> 13:25.824
Hannah:
[ GASPS ] I CAN'T DO IT.

13:25.870 --> 13:27.792
-IT'S TOO BIG.
-Bridget: YES, YOU CAN.

13:27.840 --> 13:31.207
I HAVE GO'I'I'EN BIGGER BABIES
OUT OF SMALLER GIRLS.

13:31.240 --> 13:34.209
Mary: NOT THIS BABY
OUT OF THIS GIRL,

13:34.240 --> 13:35.935
NOT UNTIL SHE TELLS US
THE NAME OF THE FATHER.

13:35.980 --> 13:38.198
Bridget:
MRS. SIBLEY, EXCUSE ME,

13:38.250 --> 13:40.844
BUT THIS BABY
HAS GOT TO COME OUT.

13:40.880 --> 13:42.541
Mary: SALEM WON'T
SHOULDER ANOTHER BASTARD.

13:42.580 --> 13:44.047
Anne: [ SCOFFS ]

13:44.090 --> 13:46.183
Mary:
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

13:46.220 --> 13:48.154
Anne:
MY FRIEND BRIDGET TEACHES ME

13:48.190 --> 13:50.283
THE WONDERS
OF GOD'S OWN CREATION.

13:50.330 --> 13:52.548
-Hannah: [ GROANING ]
-Bridget: HANNAH,

13:52.590 --> 13:54.649
WILL YOU TELL US
THE NAME OF YOUR MAN?

13:54.700 --> 13:57.396
Hannah: I CANNOT, MISS.
HE'LL LOSE HIS APPRENTICESHIP.

13:57.430 --> 14:00.490
HE AIN'T ALLOWED TO MARRY
FOR SOME YEARS YET.

14:00.540 --> 14:03.031
Mary: THAT IS HIS PROBLEM,
NOT SALEM'S.

14:03.070 --> 14:04.367
Hannah: [ GROANING ]

14:04.410 --> 14:07.402
Bridget: MARY, YOU'RE A WOMAN.

14:07.440 --> 14:10.045
YOU WERE EVEN A POOR ONE ONCE.

14:10.080 --> 14:12.139
BUT NOW YOU'RE MARY SIBLEY.

14:12.180 --> 14:14.740
FOR ONCE, USE YOUR POSITION
AMONG THE PURITANS

14:14.780 --> 14:17.908
TO HELP ONE OF YOUR OWN.

14:17.950 --> 14:19.679
Hannah: [ GROANING ]

14:21.060 --> 14:23.984
Mary:
NO MAN IS WORTH IT, CHILD,

14:24.030 --> 14:26.590
OR IF HE IS, HE WOULD RATHER
YOU TELL US HIS NAME

14:26.630 --> 14:28.291
THAN DIE TRYING TO PROTECT HIM.

14:30.630 --> 14:33.064
Hannah:
[SCREAMS,GRUNTS]

14:33.100 --> 14:34.499
BILLY!

14:34.540 --> 14:37.930
IT WAS BILLY BAILYN,
THE COOPER'S APPRENTICE.

14:37.970 --> 14:40.234
Bridget:
JUST RELAX. STAY WITH ME.

14:40.280 --> 14:41.907
-Hannah: [GROANING]
-Bridget: ALL RIGHT, HANNAH.

14:41.940 --> 14:43.840
I WANT YOU TO
GIVE ME A BIG PUSH.

14:43.880 --> 14:45.074
Hannah: [ SCREAMS ]

14:45.110 --> 14:47.044
Bridget: ALMOST THERE!

14:47.080 --> 14:49.241
-Hannah: [ SCREAMING ]
-Bridget: THAT'S IT.

14:49.280 --> 14:51.009
BIG PUSH. WELL DONE!

14:51.050 --> 14:52.745
Mary: [ GASPS ]

14:52.790 --> 14:54.610
Bridget: KEEP GOING.

14:54.660 --> 14:56.116
-Hannah: [ MOANING ]
-[ BABY CRYING ]

14:56.160 --> 14:57.957
Bridget: THAT'S IT.

14:57.990 --> 15:00.891
OH!

15:00.930 --> 15:02.966
Hannah: [ In distance ] HELP ME!

15:04.300 --> 15:07.189
[ BABY CRYING ]

15:07.240 --> 15:09.231
Woman:
IT'S GOING TO BE ALL RIGHT.

15:11.910 --> 15:14.378
EXCUSE US, MADAM.

15:14.410 --> 15:16.731
COME ON, NOW. IN YOU GO.

15:18.650 --> 15:20.413
[ BIRD CALLING ]

15:34.100 --> 15:37.024
Mr. Hale: [ PANTING ]

15:44.370 --> 15:46.008
[ GASPS ]

15:46.040 --> 15:47.803
PETRUS, REALLY.

15:47.840 --> 15:49.979
YOU OUGHT TO WEAR A LITTLE BELL.

15:50.010 --> 15:52.478
Petrus:
AND YOU, MAGISTRATE, NEED NONE.

15:52.510 --> 15:54.978
WE HEARD YOU
THE MOMENT YOU LEFI' THE ROAD.

15:55.020 --> 15:56.840
[ SNIFFING ]

15:56.880 --> 15:58.313
COME.

16:10.900 --> 16:13.198
Mr. Hale: I HAD A BIT OF TROUBLE
FINDING THE PLACE.

16:13.240 --> 16:16.368
SEEMED TO RECALL YOU HAVING BEEN
FARTHER NORTH LAST TIME.

16:16.400 --> 16:19.801
Petrus: PERHAPS I WAS,
MAGISTRATE HALE.

16:21.410 --> 16:25.301
EYES ARE FOR SEEING,

16:25.350 --> 16:28.478
NOT FOR BEING SEEN.

16:28.520 --> 16:32.286
THAT'S WHY YOUR KIND COME TO ME.

16:32.320 --> 16:36.381
YOU FIND ME WHEN YOU NEED ME.

16:36.420 --> 16:41.119
SO, WHAT DO YOU NEED?

16:41.160 --> 16:45.290
Mr. Hale: SOMEONE BROKE OUR
CIRCLE IN THE WOODS LAST NIGHT.

16:45.330 --> 16:47.662
WE NEED TO KNOW WHO SAW US.

16:47.700 --> 16:50.362
Petrus: AH. FULL BUCK MOON?

16:52.010 --> 16:54.570
UH-HUH.

17:01.380 --> 17:06.249
YOU WERE THERE THAT NIGHT,
WEREN'T YOU, LITI'LE FRIEND?

17:06.290 --> 17:09.179
TIME TO WAKE UP.

17:09.220 --> 17:12.257
WHAT DID YOU SEE?

17:19.300 --> 17:20.938
[ BLOWS ]

17:23.240 --> 17:24.707
[ CLICKING TONGUE ]

17:26.570 --> 17:29.903
[ BLOWS ]

17:32.980 --> 17:35.847
TELL MARY SIBLEY
WE WILL FIND OUT

17:35.880 --> 17:38.917
WHO WAS IN THE WOODS LAST NIGHT,

17:38.950 --> 17:42.283
BUT IT TAKES TIME.

17:44.830 --> 17:47.697
[ INDISTINCT WHISPERING ]

17:47.730 --> 17:49.550
Woman: LORD...

17:49.600 --> 17:51.397
[ SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

17:59.070 --> 18:01.129
Mary:
HAVE OUR PRAYERS BEEN ANSWERED?

18:02.410 --> 18:04.970
HAS THE POOR GIRL IMPROVED?

18:05.010 --> 18:07.570
Bridget: WE SHOULD NOT BE
PRAYING FOR GOD TO DO

18:07.620 --> 18:10.384
WHAT WE CAN ACCOMPLISH
OURSELVES.

18:10.420 --> 18:14.083
MERCY LEWIS IS NOT SUFFERING
THE WORK OF WITCHES OR DEMONS,

18:14.120 --> 18:17.487
BUT SOME NATURAL MALADY
OR FEVER OF THE MIND,

18:17.530 --> 18:20.055
YET SHE HANGS HERE
LIKE AN ANIMAL.

18:20.090 --> 18:23.821
Mary: SHE BROKE HER ROPES
THREE TIMES AT HOME,

18:23.870 --> 18:26.828
NOT TO MENTION HER FATHER'S ARM.

18:26.870 --> 18:28.838
SHE BIT OFF HER OWN FINGER

18:28.870 --> 18:31.668
-AND TEARS AT HER FLESH.
-Mercy: [GROANS]

18:31.710 --> 18:35.100
Mary: MERCY MUST BE PROTECTED
FROM HERSELF AND WE FROM HER.

18:35.140 --> 18:38.849
THERE'S NO BE'I'I'ER PLACE TO DO
BOTH THAN IN THE HOUSE OF GOD.

18:38.880 --> 18:41.815
Bridget: I THINK THE SELECTMEN
ARE EXPLOITING HER CONDITION

18:41.850 --> 18:43.511
TO CREATE FEAR IN SALEM.

18:43.550 --> 18:45.689
THIS SO-CALLED "WITCH PANIC"

18:45.720 --> 18:48.848
IS YET ANOTHER ATTEMPT
BY THE PURITANS TO CONTROL US.

18:48.890 --> 18:52.428
Mary: MISS BISHOP, PLEASE...

18:52.460 --> 18:55.190
BE CAREFUL
OF THE WORDS THAT YOU SPEAK.

18:55.230 --> 18:56.925
TO LESS SYMPATHETIC EARS,

18:56.960 --> 19:00.794
THEY COULD SOUND LIKE
THE WORDS OF THE DEVIL HIMSELF.

19:00.840 --> 19:05.800
Bridget: I'M...SORRY
IF MY WORDS WERE HARSH.

19:05.840 --> 19:09.173
SOMETIMES, MY TONGUE
RUNS AHEAD OF MY MIND.

19:09.210 --> 19:11.440
Mary: IT'S UNDERSTANDABLE.

19:11.480 --> 19:15.211
THESE ARE TRYING TIMES
FOR ALL OF US.

19:15.250 --> 19:17.218
Mercy: [ GROANS, SIGHS ]

19:24.260 --> 19:26.387
Mary: [ SNIFFLES ]

19:26.430 --> 19:29.228
Tituba: CAREFUL, MISTRESS.

19:29.260 --> 19:31.194
YOUR TEARS MAY SOUR THE MILK.

19:31.230 --> 19:32.822
Mary: THERE WAS A TIME

19:32.870 --> 19:35.839
THAT I MIGHT HAVE SUCKLED
SOMETHING OTHER THAN A TOAD.

19:35.870 --> 19:37.804
Tituba:
IT DOESN'T MATTER NOW.

19:37.840 --> 19:40.900
WHAT MATTERS IS,
WHO WILL BE NEXT?

19:40.940 --> 19:42.669
THE GRAND RITE HAS BEGUN,

19:42.710 --> 19:44.871
AND THE EARTH
CRIES OUT FOR INNOCENT BLOOD.

19:44.910 --> 19:46.571
Mary: I KNOW WELL MY DUTIES.

19:46.610 --> 19:48.248
ATTEND TO YOUR OWN.

19:48.280 --> 19:50.680
Tituba: YOUR DUTIES AND
SEEING THAT YOU FULFILL THEM

19:50.720 --> 19:53.848
IS MY DUTY, LIKE IT OR NOT.

19:53.890 --> 19:55.812
Mary: I'VE MADE MY CHOICE.

19:55.860 --> 19:58.658
BUT WE NEED
MORE THAN ANOTHER VICTIM --

19:58.690 --> 20:00.749
WE NEED A SIGN.

20:00.800 --> 20:04.258
AND I KNOW JUST THE PERSON
TO DELIVER US BOTH.

20:04.300 --> 20:08.396
OUR COTTON MATHER
IS QUITE OBSESSED WITH SIGNS --

20:08.440 --> 20:11.409
WROTE CHAPTER AND VERSE ON THEM.

20:11.440 --> 20:15.479
BUT THERE IS ONE SIGN THEY DREAD
MORE THAN ANY OTHER.

20:17.210 --> 20:19.542
THE SIGN
OF A MONSTROUS BIRTH.

20:19.580 --> 20:21.548
Tituba:
YOU WOULD DO SUCH A THING?

20:21.580 --> 20:23.343
Mary: NO, I HAVE NO NEED

20:23.390 --> 20:25.585
TO PLUCK A SINGLE LEAF
FROM THE TREE OF LIFE

20:25.620 --> 20:29.351
WHEN A LEAF
IS ALREADY DEAD ON THE BRANCH.

20:29.390 --> 20:32.257
THERE'S A GIRL OUT THERE

20:32.290 --> 20:35.555
WHO CARRIES DEATH INSIDE.

20:35.600 --> 20:38.421
I COULD SMELL THE BABY,

20:38.470 --> 20:41.359
FLOATING DEAD AND MALFORMED
IN HER MOTHER'S WOMB.

20:41.400 --> 20:43.368
DON'T WEEP FOR HER.

20:43.410 --> 20:46.766
SHE NEVER TASTED A SINGLE BITTER
BREATH OF LIFE'S BETRAYALS.

20:46.810 --> 20:49.301
YET HER BRIEF FLICKER OF LIFE

20:49.340 --> 20:51.149
WILL BURN
LIKE A COMET OVER EARTH

20:51.180 --> 20:53.819
WHEN I MAKE OF HER A SIGN...

20:53.850 --> 20:56.739
OF THE DOOM
THAT'S COME UPON SALEM.

21:03.530 --> 21:06.579
DO YOU KNOW WHAT I ENJOY MOST,
GEORGE?

21:06.630 --> 21:11.294
TURNING THE GOOD SOULS OF SALEM
AGAINST ONE ANOTHER,

21:11.330 --> 21:15.437
LIKE THE RABID DOGS
YOU TRAINED THEM TO BE.

21:15.470 --> 21:18.337
George: [ GRUNTS ] THE ONLY
THING THAT KEEPS ME ALIVE

21:18.370 --> 21:21.077
IS THE LOOK ON YOUR FACE

21:21.110 --> 21:24.841
WHEN JOHN ALDEN
FINDS OUT WHAT YOU REALLY ARE

21:24.880 --> 21:26.848
AND TH ROTTLES YOU
WITH HIS BARE HAN--

21:26.880 --> 21:28.768
[ MUFFLED SCREAMING ]

21:31.390 --> 21:34.018
[ CHOKING ]

21:34.060 --> 21:37.279
Mary: JUST THINK, GEORGE.

21:37.330 --> 21:40.128
I NEED ONLY KILL
NINE MORE INNOCENTS

21:40.160 --> 21:42.094
BEFORE FULL HUNTER'S MOON,

21:42.130 --> 21:45.065
AND MY GRAND RITE IS COMPLETE.

21:47.840 --> 21:50.707
-Kitty: [ WAILING ]
-Mab: SHH!

21:50.740 --> 21:54.176
SHH! SHUSH NOW, KITTY.

21:54.210 --> 21:56.201
IF LYING WITH OLD FAT FRED
DIDN'T KILL YOU,

21:56.240 --> 21:58.276
DELIVERING HIS CHILD WON'T,
NEITHER.

21:58.310 --> 21:59.470
Kitty: [ CRYING ]

21:59.510 --> 22:01.671
Mab: SHH!

22:01.720 --> 22:03.540
Kitty: [ GRUNTING ]

22:03.590 --> 22:06.343
[ SCREAMING ]

22:06.390 --> 22:08.210
Mab: SHH! SHH!

22:08.260 --> 22:11.650
Kitty: NO! IT FEELS LIKE
IT'LL TEAR ME IN TWO.

22:11.690 --> 22:13.453
-[ CRYING ]
-Mab: IT'S ALMOST TIME.

22:13.500 --> 22:15.559
GO FETCH BRIDGET.

22:15.600 --> 22:17.898
SHH!

22:17.930 --> 22:19.625
Kitty: [ MOANING]

22:19.670 --> 22:21.558
[ DOOR HINGES CREAK ]

22:21.600 --> 22:23.568
Gloriana:
[ GASPS ] MISS BRIDGET!

22:23.610 --> 22:25.703
I WAS JUST COMING TO GET YOU.

22:25.740 --> 22:27.537
Bridget:
I HEARD POOR KI'I'I'Y'S SCREAMS.

22:27.580 --> 22:30.231
Kitty: [ SCREAMING ]

22:30.280 --> 22:31.577
Mab: KITTY, KITTY, KITTY.

22:31.610 --> 22:33.009
-Kitty: [ SCREAMING ]
-Mab: SHH!

22:33.050 --> 22:35.143
Gloriana:
NOTHING TO FEAR NOW.

22:35.180 --> 22:37.683
MISS BRIDGET'S SEEN
MORE BABES THROUGH THE
NARROW GATE THAN ANY.

22:37.720 --> 22:40.985
Bridget:
DON'T FRET, CHILD. THE BABY'S
JUST THE WRONG WAY 'ROUND.

22:41.020 --> 22:43.682
IT IS A SIMPLE THING TO TURN IT.

22:43.730 --> 22:45.584
Kitty: [ GRUNTING ]

22:47.560 --> 22:49.551
NO! AAH!

22:49.600 --> 22:51.261
[ SCREAMING ]

22:51.300 --> 22:54.565
NO! NO! NO! NO!
[ SCREAMING ]

22:54.600 --> 22:58.104
SHE'S HURTING MY BABY!
[ SCREAMS ]

22:58.140 --> 23:00.233
AAH!

23:00.270 --> 23:01.635
[ GROANING ]

23:05.250 --> 23:07.002
[ COUGHS ]

23:07.050 --> 23:08.870
-Gloriana: [ SHUDDERS ]
-Bridget: OH!

23:16.660 --> 23:18.548
[ ANIMAL BLEATS ]

23:20.660 --> 23:23.254
Cotton: YOU WITNESSED
A REAL WITCHES' SABBAT --

23:23.300 --> 23:26.463
SOMETHING NO WITCH HUNTER HAS
EVER SEEN WITH HIS OWN EYES.

23:26.500 --> 23:29.958
ALL OF OUR IMAGES AND ACCOUNTS
COME FROM CONFESSIONS,

23:30.000 --> 23:33.003
SOME...RATHER MORE BELIEVABLE
THAN OTHERS.

23:41.820 --> 23:43.447
John: IT'S THIS ONE.

23:43.490 --> 23:44.946
Cotton: MM.

23:48.620 --> 23:52.283
IF THIS IS TRUE,
IT'S FAR WORSE THAN I THOUGHT.

23:55.830 --> 23:58.469
John: WHAT'S IT SAY?

23:58.500 --> 24:00.491
Cotton: NO LATIN, CAPTAIN?

24:00.540 --> 24:02.838
OH, OF COURSE NOT.
YOU'VE NO TIME FOR BOOKS.

24:02.870 --> 24:05.634
"RITUM MAGNI."

24:05.670 --> 24:07.604
THE GRAND RITE --

24:07.640 --> 24:10.336
THE GREATEST SECRET
OF THE WITCHES.

24:10.380 --> 24:14.168
ALL WE HAVE ARE SCRAPS
OF RUMORS OF FAILED ATTEMPTS.

24:14.220 --> 24:16.973
UNFORTUNATELY, THERE ARE
NO BOOKS BY WITCHES --
ONLY WITCH HUNTERS.

24:17.020 --> 24:18.783
John: MM.

24:18.820 --> 24:22.017
SO ALL OF THESE BOOKS...

24:22.060 --> 24:24.324
TELL YOU EXACTLY NOTHING.

24:24.360 --> 24:26.419
[ CLATTERING ]

24:26.460 --> 24:28.018
Isaac: STOP IT.

24:28.060 --> 24:30.426
YOU FIGHT EACH OTHER.
WHO FIGHTS THEM?

24:30.460 --> 24:33.020
Cotton: HE HAS A POINT.

24:33.070 --> 24:36.164
John: SO, WHERE DO WE BEGIN?

24:36.200 --> 24:40.159
Cotton: INSIDE THE TREE,
I FOUND WHAT FUELS THEIR WORK...

24:40.210 --> 24:43.543
LIKE THE WOOD OF A FIRE.

24:43.580 --> 24:46.708
SEE, EVERYTHING THE WITCH DOES
IS POWERED BY TWO THINGS --

24:46.750 --> 24:48.809
LUST AND DEATH.

24:48.850 --> 24:50.545
THE LUST
THEY PROVIDE FOR THEMSELVES,

24:50.590 --> 24:52.842
BUT THEY MUST LOOK ELSEWHERE
FOR THE DEAD PARTS.

24:52.890 --> 24:56.519
THE TOWN WOULD BE AWARE
IF THEIR OWN SALEM BURIAL GROUND

24:56.560 --> 24:59.188
WAS BEING DISTURBED
BY CORPSE GRINDING.

24:59.230 --> 25:01.323
John:
SO WHERE DO THEY GET THEM?

25:01.360 --> 25:04.193
Cotton:
ISAAC, IF YOU'D BE SO KIND

25:04.230 --> 25:06.391
AS TO EXPLAIN TO THE CAPTAIN
YOUR DUTIES.

25:06.430 --> 25:10.036
Isaac:
I GOT ALL KIND OF DUTIES --

25:10.070 --> 25:11.901
PACKAGES TO DELIVER.

25:11.940 --> 25:15.034
I ALSO DELIVER
THE UNWANTEDS TO THE CRAGS.

25:15.080 --> 25:17.901
John: THE UNWANTEDS?

25:19.750 --> 25:24.585
Isaac: YOU KNOW,
INDIANS, SLAVES, CRIMINALS --

25:24.620 --> 25:28.750
PRETTY MUCH ANYBODY AIN'T FIT
TO BE LAID IN SALEM GROUND.

25:28.790 --> 25:31.258
Cotton: THIS IS
WHERE THE WITCHES HARVEST.

25:31.290 --> 25:32.826
AND AT THE RISK
OF ANOTHER THRASHING,

25:32.860 --> 25:34.191
IT IS ALSO YOUR BEST HOPE

25:34.230 --> 25:36.391
OF RECLAIMING
YOUR FRIEND'S REMAINS.

25:36.430 --> 25:39.763
John: YOU DUMPED HIS BODY
INTO THE CRAGS?!

25:39.800 --> 25:41.939
GILES COREY
BUILT HALF THIS TOWN,

25:41.970 --> 25:44.131
AND YOU THREW HIM
INTO A GODDAMN DITCH?!

25:47.540 --> 25:49.770
LET'S GO.

25:49.810 --> 25:52.108
Cotton: WHERE?

25:52.150 --> 25:55.449
John: TO GET GILES
OUT OF THAT SHITHOLE.

25:55.480 --> 25:58.779
Mary: ALL OF SALEM
IS DIMINISHED BY YOUR LOSS.

25:58.820 --> 26:01.414
I CAN ONLY IMAGINE
YOUR SUFFERING.

26:01.460 --> 26:04.088
Kitty:
THANK YOU, MRS. SIBLEY.

26:07.290 --> 26:11.761
Mary: THE OTHERS SAID THAT
YOU WERE FRIGHTENED --

26:11.800 --> 26:15.395
YOU THOUGHT THAT SOMEONE
WAS TRYING TO HURT YOUR BABY?

26:15.440 --> 26:18.568
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED.

26:18.610 --> 26:20.669
TELL ME.

26:23.810 --> 26:27.814
I'M GOING TO
TELL YOU SOMETHING.

26:27.850 --> 26:31.411
I'VE NEVER TOLD ANYONE BEFORE.

26:35.420 --> 26:37.854
I, TOO, HAVE LOST A CHILD.

26:40.290 --> 26:42.952
OH, I KNOW THE PAIN YOU FEEL.

26:43.000 --> 26:45.662
I FEEL IT EVEN NOW.

26:48.700 --> 26:51.635
YOU MUST TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED

26:51.670 --> 26:55.504
SO THAT YOUR CHILD
DID NOT DIE IN VAIN.

26:55.540 --> 26:58.338
I PROMISE YOU...

26:58.380 --> 27:02.271
NO HARM WILL COME TO YOU.

27:02.320 --> 27:04.049
TELL ME.

27:06.320 --> 27:10.154
Kitty:
I FELT THE PRESENCE OF EVIL...

27:10.190 --> 27:13.023
AND...

27:13.060 --> 27:15.995
Mary: GO ON.

27:16.030 --> 27:20.160
Kitty: ...I SAW A FOUL HAG.

27:20.200 --> 27:22.998
AND SHE WAS TOUCHING MY BELLY.

27:23.040 --> 27:25.964
Mary: WHAT OF THE MIDWIFE?

27:27.740 --> 27:29.901
WHAT OF HER?

27:32.210 --> 27:35.008
Kitty:
THEY WERE ONE AND THE SAME.

27:38.420 --> 27:41.412
[ FLIES BUZZING ]

27:52.770 --> 27:55.796
Isaac:
TWO TIMES IN AS MANY NIGHTS?

27:55.840 --> 27:58.206
TWO TIMES TOO MANY.

27:59.910 --> 28:01.309
[ WHIMPERING ]

28:01.340 --> 28:03.570
John: SHOW ME
WHERE YOU DUMPED HIS BODY.

28:08.250 --> 28:11.378
[ BUZZING CONTINUES ]

28:11.420 --> 28:13.581
JESUS CHRIST.

28:13.620 --> 28:15.417
Isaac: [ VOMITING ]

28:15.460 --> 28:18.759
-[ COUGHS ]
-John: WHERE IS HE?

28:23.130 --> 28:24.529
Isaac: THERE.

28:32.470 --> 28:36.076
John: YOU DO NOT
LAY A HAND ON THAT MAN.

28:58.400 --> 29:00.265
Isaac: [ GRUNTING ]

29:06.140 --> 29:08.279
John: [ GRUNTING ]

29:37.000 --> 29:38.501
[ DOOR OPENS ]

29:38.540 --> 29:39.609
Cotton: [ CLEARS THROAT ]

29:39.640 --> 29:41.972
[ DOOR HINGES CREAK ]

29:42.010 --> 29:44.808
Mary: OH, FORGIVE ME.

29:44.850 --> 29:47.102
ORDINARILY,
THIS WOULD BE GEORGE'S DOMAIN,

29:47.150 --> 29:50.017
BUT MY HUSBAND --
HIS CONDITION --

29:50.050 --> 29:53.645
I FEAR THAT THE VERY SIGHT
OF THIS WOULD STOP HIS HEART.

29:53.690 --> 29:56.079
Cotton: MRS. SIBLEY, PLEASE...

29:56.120 --> 29:59.283
CALM YOURSELF.

29:59.330 --> 30:01.821
WHAT IS WRONG?

30:01.860 --> 30:05.023
Mary:
OH, A MOST TERRIBLE THING --

30:05.070 --> 30:07.026
A SIGN.

30:07.070 --> 30:09.493
Cotton: A SIGN?

30:09.540 --> 30:13.032
Mary:
YES, JUST AS YOU DESCRIBED
IN ONE OF YOUR BOOKS.

30:15.240 --> 30:17.606
A MONSTROUS BIRTH.

30:17.640 --> 30:20.177
Cotton: WHAT?

30:20.210 --> 30:22.872
HERE IN SALEM?

30:22.920 --> 30:25.445
Mary: DELIVERED BY
OUR VERY OWN MIDWIFE --

30:25.490 --> 30:27.708
BRIDGET BISHOP.

30:27.750 --> 30:31.026
Cotton: AND WHERE IS --

30:31.060 --> 30:33.893
WHAT HAS BECOME OF
THIS MONSTER NOW? WHERE IS IT?

30:33.930 --> 30:36.353
Mary: IN THIS VERY ROOM.

30:36.400 --> 30:39.289
MR. LAMB FLOATED IT
IN A BOTTLE. I...

30:39.330 --> 30:41.264
[ SIGHS ]

30:51.250 --> 30:54.242
Cotton:
BY THE WOUNDS OF CHRIST!

30:54.280 --> 30:57.545
THE MERE SIGHT OF THIS WOULD
PIERCE OUR DEAR LORD YET AGAIN!

30:57.580 --> 31:00.219
YOU WERE RIGHT TO SEND FOR ME.

31:00.250 --> 31:03.549
THIS IS MOST TERRIBLE.

31:03.590 --> 31:06.184
Mary:
BUT WHAT DOES IT PORTEND?

31:06.230 --> 31:08.027
WHAT IS THIS A SIGN OF?

31:08.060 --> 31:10.494
Cotton:
THERE CAN BE NO DOUBT.

31:10.530 --> 31:13.931
'TIS NOTHING LESS THAN
A DECLARATION OF WAR UPON US

31:13.970 --> 31:17.235
BY THE DEVIL HIMSELF.

31:17.270 --> 31:19.033
Mary: [ BREATHES SHARPLY]

31:22.080 --> 31:24.742
REVEREND...

31:24.780 --> 31:27.806
IS THERE ANYTHING WE CAN DO?

31:29.880 --> 31:32.019
Cotton: I WILL DO
WHATEVER IS IN MY POWER

31:32.050 --> 31:35.611
TO PROTECT SALEM...

31:35.660 --> 31:37.582
AND YOU, MADAM.

31:37.620 --> 31:42.250
Mary: I THANK GOD YOU'RE HERE,
REVEREND.

31:42.300 --> 31:44.894
WE WOULD BE LOST WITHOUT YOU.

31:53.070 --> 31:54.571
[ BELLS TOLLING ]

31:54.610 --> 31:56.601
Anne: FATHER, PLEASE WAIT.

31:56.640 --> 31:58.870
[ PANTING ]

31:58.910 --> 32:01.242
FATHER, YOU KNOW BRIDGET.

32:01.280 --> 32:03.874
HOW COULD YOU
THINK HER GUILTY OF THIS?

32:03.920 --> 32:06.480
Mr. Hale: IT ISN'T
A MATTER OF WHAT I THINK.

32:06.520 --> 32:07.919
Anne: FATHER.

32:07.960 --> 32:10.110
John: ANOTHER RUSH TO JUDGMENT,
MATHER?

32:10.160 --> 32:12.583
Cotton:
QUITE THE CONTRARY, I FEAR.

32:12.630 --> 32:16.157
IT IS JUDGMENT THAT IS
RUSHING TOWARDS ALL OF US.

32:16.200 --> 32:19.795
BEHOLD THE WARRANT OF JUDGMENT.

32:19.830 --> 32:25.939
FOR OUR SINS,
INDIVIDUAL AND COLLECTIVE,

32:25.970 --> 32:29.178
HE HAS SIGNED
THE SEAL OF SATAN,

32:29.210 --> 32:31.474
A MESSAGE STRAIGHT FROM HELL

32:31.510 --> 32:34.149
TO HERALD THE ARRIVAL
OF THE DEVIL IN SALEM.

32:34.180 --> 32:36.671
AND WHO DELIVERED HIS MESSAGE
FOR HIM?

32:36.720 --> 32:39.280
BRIDGET BISHOP.

32:39.320 --> 32:42.357
DID YOU OR DID YOU NOT

32:42.390 --> 32:45.689
DELIVER THIS MONSTER
FROM THAT GIRL?

32:45.730 --> 32:47.459
Bridget: YES, BUT --

32:47.490 --> 32:49.321
Cotton:
DID YOU OR DID YOU NOT

32:49.360 --> 32:51.863
MINISTER TO THIS GIRL
WHILE SHE CARRIED IT?

32:51.900 --> 32:53.162
Bridget:
YES, SIR, BUT I MINISTER --

32:53.200 --> 32:55.691
Cotton: DID YOU OR DID YOU NOT

32:55.740 --> 33:00.029
FREQUENTLY DOSE HER
WITH PHYSICS AND POTIONS

33:00.070 --> 33:02.971
AND HERBAL CONCOCTIONS
OF YOUR OWN DEVISING?

33:03.010 --> 33:05.001
Bridget: SIR, THAT IS WHAT I DO,
BUT I DID NOT --

33:05.050 --> 33:07.177
Cotton:
AND DID YOU OR DID YOU NOT
PLACE YOUR HANDS UPON HER BELLY,

33:07.210 --> 33:10.043
PRESSING THIS WAY AND THAT

33:10.080 --> 33:12.014
JUST BEFORE THE THING CAME OUT?

33:12.050 --> 33:13.711
Bridget:
I WAS TURNING THE BABE SO --

33:13.750 --> 33:16.878
Cotton:
AYE, BUT TURNING IT INTO WHAT?

33:16.920 --> 33:19.127
Anne: STOP!
[AUDIENCE MURMURING ]

33:19.160 --> 33:20.980
WHATEVER
THAT POOR STONE CHILD MAY BE,

33:21.030 --> 33:22.827
YOU ARE THE TRUE MONSTER!

33:25.400 --> 33:27.721
Mr. Hale:
I APOLOGIZE FOR MY DAUGHTER.

33:27.770 --> 33:30.068
THE ACCUSED
IS A DEAR FRIEND OF HERS.

33:30.100 --> 33:33.069
BUT I SHARE HER CONCERN.

33:33.110 --> 33:34.407
YOU WOULD ACCUSE A WOMAN --

33:34.440 --> 33:37.705
A WOMAN
WHOM WE ALL KNOW AND TRUST,

33:37.740 --> 33:40.004
WHO NEVER DID ANYTHING
BUT HELP OTHER WOMEN

33:40.050 --> 33:44.248
TO DELIVER THEIR BABIES AND CARE
FOR THOSE WHO NO ONE WANTED?

33:44.290 --> 33:48.078
AND NOW, SUDDENLY,
WE'RE TO BELIEVE SHE'S A WITCH?

33:48.120 --> 33:50.418
Cotton:
THE DEVIL IS PATIENT.

33:53.190 --> 33:55.750
AND SO ARE HIS SERVANTS --

33:55.800 --> 33:59.827
OUR FRIENDS, OUR NEIGHBORS --

33:59.870 --> 34:04.239
TILL, FINALLY,
THEY ARE CALLED TO SERVE HIM.

34:04.270 --> 34:06.409
BRIDGET BISHOP,

34:06.440 --> 34:08.738
YOU HAVE DELIVERED A MONSTER
INTO THE WORLD.

34:08.780 --> 34:11.248
YOU WERE SEEN
IN YOUR TRUE GUISE,

34:11.280 --> 34:13.248
THE NIGHT HAG, BY YOUR VICTIM.

34:13.280 --> 34:15.419
AND EVEN THOSE WHO WERE DUPED
BY YOUR INNOCENT IMAGE

34:15.450 --> 34:19.238
COULD STILL SENSE THE PALPABLE
STENCH OF EVIL AROUND THEM

34:19.290 --> 34:24.785
AS YOU DESTROYED A BABE
IN THE CRADLE OF LIFE --

34:24.830 --> 34:30.655
A SIGN OF YOUR MASTER'S
DECLARATION OF WAR UPON US.

34:32.900 --> 34:34.458
HOW DO YOU PLEAD?

34:34.500 --> 34:39.267
Bridget:
I DID NO SUCH THING.

34:39.310 --> 34:41.130
I'M INNOCENT!

34:41.180 --> 34:43.478
OH, YOU MUST BELIVE ME --
I AM --

34:43.510 --> 34:45.899
John:
I'M A LITTLE CONFUSED, MATHER.

34:47.250 --> 34:49.468
DID BRIDGET MAKE THAT SIGN...

34:49.520 --> 34:51.317
OR DID GOD?

34:51.350 --> 34:54.478
NO. NO, NO, NO.
WAIT. I REMEMBER.

34:54.520 --> 34:56.613
GOD TOLD THE DEVIL,
AND THE DEVIL MADE HER DO IT --

34:56.660 --> 34:58.719
HAVE I GOT THIS RIGHT?

34:58.760 --> 35:01.888
NO? MAYBE I'M JUST
NOT AS SMART AS YOU.

35:01.930 --> 35:04.091
I HAVEN'T READ ALL THOSE BOOKS,

35:04.130 --> 35:06.769
BUT I HAVE SEEN A FEW THINGS
IN THE WORLD.

35:06.800 --> 35:09.963
AND IN THIS WORLD,
BAD THINGS HAPPEN,

35:10.000 --> 35:15.176
GENERALLY WITH NO MORE MEANING
THAN THE ROLL OF A DICE.

35:15.210 --> 35:19.249
Cotton: THIS MONSTROSITY --

35:19.280 --> 35:22.647
IT'S JUST
AN UNLUCKY ROLL OF GOD'S DICE?

35:22.680 --> 35:24.739
John: PROBABLY
THE UNLUCKIEST I'VE SEEN.

35:24.790 --> 35:26.519
Cotton: WELL, THEN,
WE HAVE A MOST PROFOUND
DIFFERENCE OF OPINION.

35:26.550 --> 35:28.086
John: WE DO.

35:28.120 --> 35:30.759
BUT YOU WOULD
HANG A WOMAN ON YOUR OPINION.

35:30.790 --> 35:33.657
Cotton:
AND ON YOURS, YOU WOULD LET
AN AGENT OF THE DEVIL HIMSELF

35:33.690 --> 35:36.193
WALK FREE TO DO MORE MALICE.

35:38.530 --> 35:40.998
John:
THEN PUT HER ON TRIAL, TOO.

35:41.030 --> 35:43.191
DON'T JUST STOP THERE.

35:43.240 --> 35:44.309
THERE WERE OTHERS WITH HER.

35:44.340 --> 35:46.661
OR MAYBE
THEY'RE ALL RESPONSIBLE.

35:46.710 --> 35:49.508
Gloriana: NO, YOU CAN'T!
IT'S NOT MY FAULT!

35:49.540 --> 35:50.768
John: IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT?

35:50.810 --> 35:53.005
NO, I THINK THAT
YOU'RE PROBABLY RIGHT.

35:53.050 --> 35:55.211
I THINK -- AND I KNOW THIS IS
UNTHINKABLE TO YOU, MATHER --

35:55.250 --> 35:58.686
BUT MAYBE, JUST MAYBE,
IT'S NO ONE'S FAULT.

35:58.720 --> 36:00.017
[ AUDIENCE MURMURING ]

36:00.050 --> 36:03.884
WE ALL KNOW THAT
KILLING IS DIFFERENT.

36:03.920 --> 36:07.151
KILLING
IS ALWAYS SOMEONE'S FAULT.

36:07.190 --> 36:11.024
THE STONES AREN'T DRY
FROM THE BLOOD OF GILES COREY,

36:11.060 --> 36:12.561
AND NOW YOU ARE
WILLING TO HANG A WOMAN --

36:12.600 --> 36:14.795
THIS WOMAN, BRIDGET BISHOP --

36:14.840 --> 36:17.058
AND, HELL, THROW IN
A FEW WHORES FOR GOOD MEASURE --

36:17.100 --> 36:19.034
AND FOR WHAT?

36:19.070 --> 36:21.231
[ AUDIENCE MURMURING ]

36:31.790 --> 36:34.179
Mary: PERHAPS IT'S TIME
WE HEARD FROM MERCY.

36:34.220 --> 36:36.017
ISN'T THAT RIGHT,
REVEREND MATHER?

36:36.060 --> 36:37.584
ISN'T SHE BOUND TO REACT

36:37.620 --> 36:40.589
IN FRONT OF
THE GUILTY WITCH OR WITCHES?

36:40.630 --> 36:43.724
Cotton: MY FATHER
AND ALL THE EXPERTS AGREE --

36:43.760 --> 36:45.193
Mary: THEN TAKE THEM TO HER.

36:46.530 --> 36:47.827
Cotton: THEM?

36:47.870 --> 36:50.532
Mary:
CAPTAIN ALDEN IS QUITE RIGHT.

36:50.570 --> 36:52.709
ALL MAY BE GUILTY.

36:52.740 --> 36:55.573
TAKE THE MIDWIFE
AND THE THREE WHORES, TOO.

36:55.610 --> 36:57.532
[ AUDIENCE MURMURING ]

37:03.480 --> 37:04.947
Mercy: [ GROANS ]

37:10.460 --> 37:12.052
[ GROANS ]

37:17.300 --> 37:19.393
[ GROANS ]

37:24.640 --> 37:27.006
Bridget: [ GASPS ]

37:29.140 --> 37:31.745
Mercy: [ GROANS ]

37:33.110 --> 37:35.146
Bridget: [ SCREAMING ]

37:37.120 --> 37:39.509
[ CRYING ]

37:44.160 --> 37:46.549
Mary: SHALL WE VOTE?

37:52.130 --> 37:54.360
Bridget: [ GASPING ]

37:57.100 --> 37:59.466
[ CRYING ]

37:59.510 --> 38:01.501
LORD...

38:01.540 --> 38:05.499
YOU WHO SEES
AND KNOWS OUR SECRET HEARTS

38:05.550 --> 38:09.338
MUST KNOW THAT I AM INNOCENT.

38:09.380 --> 38:13.089
PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE GIVE THEM

38:13.120 --> 38:16.988
SOME VISIBLE SIGN
OF THIS SIMPLE TRUTH.

38:17.020 --> 38:19.454
PLEASE.

38:23.060 --> 38:27.064
[ SOBBING ]

38:28.130 --> 38:29.199
[ GASPS ]

38:29.240 --> 38:30.969
[ ROPE CREAKS ]

38:31.000 --> 38:32.365
[ CHOKING ]

38:49.590 --> 38:52.650
[ BIRD CAWING ]

38:57.900 --> 39:00.494
John: WELL DONE.

39:00.530 --> 39:03.533
ANOTHER INNOCENT KILLED.

39:03.570 --> 39:06.038
Cotton: I DO NOT THINK SO.

39:06.070 --> 39:08.538
BUT EVEN IF I DID...

39:08.580 --> 39:12.573
LET THE LORD ADD IT
TO MY ALREADY LENGTHY
LIST OF MORTAL SINS.

39:12.610 --> 39:16.319
I MUST PAY ANY PRICE,

39:16.350 --> 39:19.717
SPILL MY OWN OR ANY OTHER'S
BLOOD TO STOP THE WITCHES.

39:19.750 --> 39:21.752
John: I DON'T THINK
I'VE EVER SEEN SUCH A MIXTURE

39:21.790 --> 39:24.156
OF REASON AND BULLSHIT IN A MAN.

39:24.190 --> 39:27.887
Cotton:
IF YOU ONLY KNEW WHAT I KNOW...

39:27.930 --> 39:29.249
John: WHAT?

39:29.300 --> 39:32.189
I'D CRUSH A MAN OR HANG A WOMAN,

39:32.230 --> 39:33.822
THEN DRINK MYSELF BLIND

39:33.870 --> 39:36.259
AND BURY MYSELF INTO A WHORE
LIKE THERE'S NO TOMORROW?

39:36.300 --> 39:38.188
Cotton: IF WE DO NOT
STOP THESE FOUL HAGS,

39:38.240 --> 39:40.333
THERE WILL BE NO TOMORR--

39:40.370 --> 39:42.679
Anne: YOU MONSTER!

39:42.710 --> 39:44.029
-John: STOP!
-Anne: [ GRUNTING ]

39:44.080 --> 39:46.071
Mr. Hale: WHAT A MESS
YOU'VE MADE OF THINGS.

39:46.110 --> 39:48.749
WE WERE NEARLY RUINED
BY A SINGLE SOUND ARGUMENT

39:48.780 --> 39:50.873
FROM A MAN
YOU CAN'T SEEM TO LET ALONE.

39:50.920 --> 39:53.411
I QUESTION NOW
WHY WE LET YOU BEGIN THIS.

39:53.450 --> 39:55.088
Mary: WHY?

39:55.120 --> 39:58.089
BECAUSE THIS IS THE FULFILLMENT
OF ALL OUR DREAMS --

39:58.120 --> 40:00.725
VENGEANCE
FOR CENTURIES OF OPPRESSION.

40:00.760 --> 40:03.228
TOO LATE FOR DOUBTS NOW, HALE.

40:03.260 --> 40:05.091
WE ARE ALL IN THIS TOGETHER.

40:05.130 --> 40:08.065
Mr. Hale: YES, AND WE SHALL ALL
BURN TOGETHER AT THIS RATE.

40:08.100 --> 40:10.933
YOU'RE TOO YOUNG TO UNDERSTAND
THE RISK YOU'RE TAKING.

40:10.970 --> 40:15.100
I SAW MY ENTIRE FAMILY
BURNED AT THE STAKE.

40:15.140 --> 40:17.108
I TASTED THEIR ASHES
IN MY MOUTH.

40:17.140 --> 40:19.938
I HAVE NO DESIRE
TO TASTE MY OWN...

40:19.980 --> 40:22.642
-OR MY DAUGHTER'S.
-Anne: [CRYING ]

40:22.680 --> 40:25.547
Mary: WELL, PERHAPS
YOU OLD-WORLD WITCHES

40:25.590 --> 40:28.479
ARE SIMPLY TOO SCARED --
OR TOO SCARRED --

40:28.520 --> 40:30.579
TO CLAIM THIS NEW WORLD.

40:30.620 --> 40:32.121
NOT ME.

40:32.160 --> 40:33.650
Mr. Hale: I'M NOT ALONE.

40:33.690 --> 40:36.295
THE ELDERS
HAVE THEIR DOUBTS, TOO.

40:36.330 --> 40:40.118
Mary:
ALL YOUR FEARS ARE UNNECESSARY.

40:40.170 --> 40:42.991
INNOCENT BLOOD FLOWS
AND WILL CONTINUE TO FLOW.

40:43.040 --> 40:47.067
RESULTS, MR. HALE,
ARE ALL THAT MATTER.

40:47.110 --> 40:49.931
AND SPEAKING OF RESULTS,

40:49.980 --> 40:52.073
WHAT OF YOUR ERRAND?

40:52.110 --> 40:55.841
Mr. Hale: PETRUS ASSURES US
WE'LL SOON KNOW WHO SAW US.

40:55.880 --> 40:57.609
Mary: HM.

40:57.650 --> 41:00.118
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

41:01.190 --> 41:03.317
Petrus: [ HUMMING ]

41:39.890 --> 41:43.189
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

41:43.230 --> 41:45.698
Lamb:
OH, UM...SORRY, MISS HALE,

41:45.730 --> 41:47.391
BUT, UH, YOU KNOW THE RULES.

41:47.430 --> 41:50.866
THERE'S, UH,
NO WOMEN ALLOWED AFTER DARK.

41:50.900 --> 41:53.209
John: IT'S ALL RIGHT, LAMB.

41:53.240 --> 41:56.004
ACCORDING TO MATHER,
THESE ARE THE END TIMES.

41:56.040 --> 41:59.168
I THINK WE CAN
MAKE AN EXCEPTION FOR TONIGHT.

42:07.250 --> 42:09.912
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

42:11.460 --> 42:13.758
Anne:
YOU'RE JUST LIKE THEM --

42:13.790 --> 42:15.724
HAPPY TO DISCUSS AND DEBATE,

42:15.760 --> 42:18.422
BUT TOO AFRAID
TO TAKE ANY REAL ACTION.

42:19.900 --> 42:22.539
WHY ARE YOU EVEN IN SALEM?

42:25.110 --> 42:27.761
WHERE'S THAT FIRE
I SAW IN YOUR EYES

42:27.810 --> 42:30.108
THE NIGHT
THEY KILLED YOUR FRIEND?

42:30.980 --> 42:32.277
[ TABLE THUDS ]
[ GASPS ]

42:32.310 --> 42:34.278
John: WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME,
MISS HALE?

42:34.310 --> 42:36.619
Anne: JUSTICE --

42:36.650 --> 42:40.108
FOR GILES COREY,
FOR BRIDGET BISHOP,

42:40.150 --> 42:42.209
AND FOR ALL THE OTHER
INNOCENT VICTIMS

42:42.260 --> 42:44.649
SOON TO COME FROM THIS MADNESS.

42:45.930 --> 42:48.490
SOMEONE MUST DO SOMETHING!

42:53.670 --> 42:55.661
WHAT?

42:58.270 --> 43:01.433
John: YOU JUST REMIND ME
OF SOMEONE I ONCE KNEW.

43:01.470 --> 43:04.268
Anne: WHAT HAPPENED TO THEM?

43:07.410 --> 43:10.140
John: I WISH I KNEW.

43:10.180 --> 43:12.683
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

43:18.490 --> 43:20.629
Mary: HERE UNINVITED --

43:20.660 --> 43:23.754
YOU MUST HAVE STAYED TOO LONG
WITH THE INDIANS.

43:23.800 --> 43:27.065
IT'S MADE YOU MORE...SAVAGE.

43:27.100 --> 43:30.831
John: NO. LESS PATIENT.

43:32.170 --> 43:34.161
THERE'S SOMETHING
I THINK YOU SHOULD KNOW.

43:34.210 --> 43:35.939
-Mary: YOU'RE LEAVING SALEM?
-John: TO THE CONTRARY.

43:35.980 --> 43:38.972
ANNE HALE REMINDED ME
SALEM DESERVES BETTER.

43:39.010 --> 43:40.739
IT ALWAYS DID.

43:40.780 --> 43:42.145
Mary: REALLY?

43:42.180 --> 43:44.148
I THOUGHT YOU HATED THIS PLACE.

43:44.180 --> 43:46.011
John: I THOUGHT SO, TOO.

43:46.050 --> 43:49.417
BUT IT TURNS OUT
IT WASN'T SALEM THAT I HATED --

43:49.460 --> 43:51.781
RATHER, THE PEOPLE WHO RUN IT.

43:53.630 --> 43:56.827
FELLA TOLD ME SOMETHING
TODAY -- HE SAID IT WAS
A DAMN SIGHT EASIER

43:56.860 --> 44:00.193
TO BREAK THINGS
THAN TO FIX THEM.

44:00.230 --> 44:02.698
Mary:
AND YOU INTEND TO FIX THINGS.

44:02.740 --> 44:04.162
John: MAYBE.

44:04.200 --> 44:07.328
Mary:
HOW DO YOU PLAN ON DOING THAT?

44:07.370 --> 44:11.534
John: THERE'S AN EXTRA SEAT
ON THE BOARD OF SELECT MEN --

44:11.580 --> 44:16.142
A SEAT WITH THE ALDEN NAME.

44:16.180 --> 44:19.638
RECKONED
MAYBE IT WAS TIME I CLAIMED IT.

44:19.690 --> 44:23.012
MIGHT JUST BE ONE VOICE,

44:23.060 --> 44:25.927
BUT IT IS A START.

44:32.270 --> 44:35.239
[ DOOR OPENS ]
Tituba: [ CLEARS THROAT ]

44:39.510 --> 44:41.159
John: I'LL BE SEEING YOU.

45:14.040 --> 45:16.577
[ MOUSE SQUEAKING ]

45:24.950 --> 45:27.441
[ SQUEAKING CONTINUES ]

45:27.490 --> 45:28.855
[ MOUSE SQUEALS ]

45:28.890 --> 45:31.154
[ BLOOD DRIPPING ]

45:41.970 --> 45:44.768
[ CRUNCHING ]

46:16.000 --> 46:19.504
[ DOOR HINGES CREAKING ]

46:25.050 --> 46:27.678
[ TAPPING ]

46:33.320 --> 46:34.958
Anne: GO AWAY, CAT.

46:34.990 --> 46:37.550
YOU'LL RUIN MY WORK.

46:42.060 --> 46:43.698
[ SCRAPE ]
